      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "====>"              to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-150.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se visualizzazione linea a blanks               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se visualizzazione numero linea a spaces        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-lin-imm-num-lin      .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-900.
       vis-lin-cor-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
