           move      w-rig-cod-fnt-rag    to   w-lin-imm-rag-fnt      .
       vis-lin-cor-490.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si/no da verificare                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-snx-dav        =    spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-lin-imm-snx-dav
           else      move  "*"            to   w-lin-imm-snx-dav      .
       vis-lin-cor-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing Numero documento                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bft-num-doc       to   w-lin-imm-num-doc      .
